"content": "<p>The date of the offering of firstfruits, a celebration of God's gift of the harvest, is not clear; it was probably held on 16th Abib.</p>\n<h2>Offerings made at the celebration of the firstfruits</h2>\n<h3>A burnt offering and a grain offering</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:12-Lev23:13\">LEV 23:12–23:13</a></p>\n<h3>Other offerings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:19-Lev23:20\">LEV 23:19–23:20</a></p>",
